97
00:06:12,990 --> 00:06:15,670
♪ There's a river ♪
<font color="#afddff">Kỷ niệm thuở nào</font>

98
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:19,170
♪ Full of memory ♪
<font color="#afddff">Khúc sông sâu còn vương</font>

99
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:23,770
♪ Sleep, my darlings, safe and sound ♪
<font color="#afddff">Khép mi mau dệt mộng chiêm bao</font>

100
00:06:24,070 --> 00:06:30,150
♪ For in this river all is found ♪
<font color="#afddff">Ký ức sông sâu, lại về bên ta</font>

101
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:34,810
♪ In her waters ♪
<font color="#afddff">Nhìn con nước kìa</font>

102
00:06:34,810 --> 00:06:37,650
♪ Deep and true ♪
<font color="#afddff">Sâu thật sâu</font>

103
00:06:37,910 --> 00:06:40,750
♪ Lie the answers ♪
<font color="#afddff">Và mang những điều</font>

104
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:43,750
♪ And a path for you ♪
<font color="#afddff">Dắt con quay về mau</font>

105
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:48,010
♪ Dive down deep into her sound ♪
<font color="#afddff">Đắm trong bao gọi mời xôn xao</font>

106
00:06:48,170 --> 00:06:53,430
♪ But not too far or you'll be drowned ♪
<font color="#afddff">Chớ có quá lâu để mình lao đao</font>

107
00:06:55,710 --> 00:07:01,510
♪ Yes she will sing to those who hear ♪
<font color="#afddff">Lời ca vang đến ai đang mong chờ</font>

108
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:07,810
♪ And in her song all magic flows ♪
<font color="#afddff">Để thấy nhân gian nhiệm màu bao nhiêu</font>

109
00:07:08,170 --> 00:07:13,530
♪ But can you brave what you most fear ♪
<font color="#afddff">Và con có dám bước qua cơn sợ</font>

110
00:07:13,610 --> 00:07:18,030
♪ Can you face what the river knows? ♪
<font color="#afddff">Trước gian nan liệu lòng con có chắc?</font>

